      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "New York 4, New York FLYING DISCS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "For the information of the Bureau, on August 27, 1952,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "the Newark division received a request from the Inspector General,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "United States Air Force, 2nd District Office of Special Investi-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "gations, 67 Broad Street, New York 4, New York, that the back-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "ground of a civilian photographer, [REDACTED] Passaic,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "N. J., be investigated in an attempt to determine their reliability",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "in view of the fact that they had allegedly observed and photo-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "graphed an unidentified aerial object on July 31, 1952.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "The appropriate credit and criminal checks were made in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "this matter as well as discreet neighborhood inquiries as to both",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "individuals and no information was received that either individual",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "had criminal records or that they were known in the past to have",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "perpetrated any kind of fraud.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "It was ascertained that [REDACTED] did photograph an allegedly",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "unidentified aerial object and that [REDACTED] witnessed the incident",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "and developed and printed the exposed film which was subsequently",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "forwarded to the 5th OSI District, Air Technical Intelligence",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "Center, Wright-Patterson Air Force Base, Ohio by Mr. [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "staff writer, \"The Herald News, Passaic, N. J.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "The letter further requested that the photographer and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "the witness be questioned as to the circumstances under which the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "photographs were taken and that an attempt be made to locate",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "other sources in the area that might determine the authenticity",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "of the photos. No investigation of this type was made by the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "Newark division.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "In accordance with SAC letter #83, Series 1952 dated",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
